        "<p><span class=\"math\">\\[\\begin{aligned}\n\\lim_{x \\rightarrow 0}\\frac{\\sqrt{x + 1} - 1}{x} &amp;= \\lim_{x \\rightarrow 0}\\frac{\\sqrt{x + 1} - 1}{x}\\times \\frac{\\sqrt{x + 1} + 1}{\\sqrt{x + 1} + 1} \\\\\n&amp;= \\lim_{x \\rightarrow 0}\\frac{x + 1 - 1}{x(\\sqrt{x + 1} + 1)}\\\\\n&amp;= \\lim_{x \\rightarrow 0}\\frac{x}{x(\\sqrt{x + 1} + 1)}\\\\\n&amp;= \\lim_{x \\rightarrow 0}\\frac{1}{\\sqrt{x + 1} + 1}\\\\\n&amp;= \\frac{1}{2}\\end{aligned}\\]</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"math\">\\[\\begin{aligned}\n{\\color{blue}\\mbox{Therefore, }\\lim_{x \\rightarrow 0}\\frac{\\sqrt{x + 1} - 1}{x} =\\frac{1}{2}}\\end{aligned}\\]</span></p>\n"
    ], 
    "sols_latex": [
